  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A top-down arena shooter where you play a mercenary fighting against the legions of Santa. Santa has gone ROGUE. He is not paying the Elves, contributing to global warming, and using sweatshops to produce extra presents to save on costs. You have been hired by the United Nations to fight his legions, because they are afraid of a PR nightmare.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a very classic Arcade game. Simple controls, instant action, short play sessions, and a leaderboard for the global Top 10. Slay Santa's minions while enjoying some smooth Jazz.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are three types of soldiers in the legions of Santa. Elves, Reindeer, and Mall Santas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/0194e37f468c5ed0c5d9677fd9f27d28.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/a0d2e114172d49d5c8791a63e1bfc0e4.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/0bf99dc0d5c37fe67fa193092ab4d2de.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A top-down arena shooter where you play a mercenary fighting against the legions of Santa. Santa has gone ROGUE. He is not paying the Elves, contributing to global warming, and using sweatshops to produce extra presents to save on costs. You have been hired by the United Nations to fight his legions, because they are afraid of a PR nightmare.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a very classic Arcade game. Simple controls, instant action, short play sessions, and a leaderboard for the global Top 10. Slay Santa's minions while enjoying some smooth Jazz.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are three types of soldiers in the legions of Santa. Elves, Reindeer, and Mall Santas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/0194e37f468c5ed0c5d9677fd9f27d28.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/a0d2e114172d49d5c8791a63e1bfc0e4.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3540230/extras/0bf99dc0d5c37fe67fa193092ab4d2de.avif?t=1744383734\" width=74 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
